{"type":"message","id":"76911d22","parentId":"a52c7e6c","timestamp":"2026-04-22T17:12:03.962Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"222180620","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Usage: opencli eastmoney [options] [command]\n\neastmoney commands\n\nOptions:\n  -h, --help                  display help for command\n\nCommands:\n  announcement [options]      上市公司公告（按交易所筛选）\n  convertible [options]       可转债行情列表（默认按成交额排序）\n  etf [options]               ETF 列表按成交额/涨跌幅排行\n  holders [options] <symbol>  十大流通股东（A股 F10 数据）\n  hot-rank [options]          东方财富热股榜\n  index-board [options]       主要市场指数行情（A股 / 港股 / 美股）\n  kline [options] <symbol>    K线历史数据（分/日/周/月/前复权/后复权）\n  kuaixun [options]           东方财富 7x24 财经快讯\n  longhu [options]            龙虎榜明细（A股交易所公开披露榜单）\n  money-flow [options]        主力资金净流入排行（今日/5日/10日）\n  northbound [options]        沪深港通北向/南向资金当日分时净流入（万元）\n  quote [options] <symbols>   个股实时行情（A股 / 港股 / 美股）— 来自 push2.eastmoney.com\n  rank [options]              东财市场涨跌/成交排行（沪深/北证/创/科/港/美）\n  sectors [options]           板块排行（行业/概念/地域）按涨跌幅、主力资金或成交额排序\n  help [command]              display help for command"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":7344,"aggregated":"Usage: opencli eastmoney [options] [command]\n\neastmoney commands\n\nOptions:\n  -h, --help                  display help for command\n\nCommands:\n  announcement [options]      上市公司公告（按交易所筛选）\n  convertible [options]       可转债行情列表（默认按成交额排序）\n  etf [options]               ETF 列表按成交额/涨跌幅排行\n  holders [options] <symbol>  十大流通股东（A股 F10 数据）\n  hot-rank [options]          东方财富热股榜\n  index-board [options]       主要市场指数行情（A股 / 港股 / 美股）\n  kline [options] <symbol>    K线历史数据（分/日/周/月/前复权/后复权）\n  kuaixun [options]           东方财富 7x24 财经快讯\n  longhu [options]            龙虎榜明细（A股交易所公开披露榜单）\n  money-flow [options]        主力资金净流入排行（今日/5日/10日）\n  northbound [options]        沪深港通北向/南向资金当日分时净流入（万元）\n  quote [options] <symbols>   个股实时行情（A股 / 港股 / 美股）— 来自 push2.eastmoney.com\n  rank [options]              东财市场涨跌/成交排行（沪深/北证/创/科/港/美）\n  sectors [options]           板块排行（行业/概念/地域）按涨跌幅、主力资金或成交额排序\n  help [command]              display help for command","cwd":"/home/kensoulstar/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776877923955}}
