{"type":"message","id":"72274472","parentId":"e9303077","timestamp":"2026-04-22T17:16:17.872Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The text is garbled because the encoding conversion didn't work properly. Let me try a different approach - use Python to handle the GB2312/GBK encoding properly, or try to get the raw content and decode it better.\n\nLet me also try to extract specific information like company name, registration date, capital, etc. from the HTML source.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"480888214","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"curl -sL --connect-timeout 15 \"https://www.lwty.com/Single_index_id_1.shtml\" | python3 -c \"\nimport sys\nimport re\ncontent = sys.stdin.read()\n\n# Try to find Chinese text patterns\nchinese_pattern = re.compile(r'[\\u4e00-\\u9fff]{2,}')\n\n# Extract all Chinese text segments\nsegments = chinese_pattern.findall(content)\n\n# Print unique meaningful segments (skip very short ones)\nseen = set()\nfor seg in segments:\n    if len(seg) > 10 and seg not in seen:\n        seen.add(seg)\n        print(seg)\n\" 2>/dev/null | head -60","timeout":20}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"lmstudio","model":"qwen3.6-35b-a3b-claude-4.6-opus-reasoning-distilled@q4_k_m","usage":{"input":43578,"output":342,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":43920,"cost":{"input":0.087156,"output":0.004104,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.09126}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776878167728,"responseId":"chatcmpl-yhzpu9ucvrcxi65iul8rh"}}
{"type":"message","id":"352c644b","parentId":"72274472","timestamp":"2026-04-22T17:16:18.227Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"480888214","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"四川里伍铜业股份有限公司\n四川里伍铜业股份有限公司前身为四川省里伍铜矿\n系由甘孜州国资委实际控制的国有控股企业\n公司主要从事有色金属采选\n销售并兼营水电资源的开发\n公司主营业务为自有铜矿开采及选矿业务\n公司注册地址及办公总部设在康定\n主体矿山位于甘孜藏族自治州九龙县魁多镇\n公司总部下设十个职能部门\n一座直属矿山和一个项目部\n丹巴协作铂镍公司等五家子公司及一家参股商业银行\n其中大专及以上学历的员工\n公司以其良好的经营业绩成为甘孜州的纳税大户\n进入四川省工业企业最大规模\n四川省工业企业最佳效益\n全国危机矿山接替资源找矿专项先进集体\n公司所属的里伍铜矿被四川省人民政府授予四川省重点建设先进单位称号\n中国地质调查局地质科技奖二等奖\n年度科技创新工作先进单位\n年度四川省企业技术中心\n公司控股子公司雅砻江矿业被评为\n公司拥有的里伍铜矿和黑牛洞铜矿均被自然资源部纳入全国绿色矿山名录\n利用自身在资源开发上的人才\n运作好更多优势的开发项目\n把企业进一步做强做优做大\n使里伍公司长期繁荣昌盛\n为富民安康做出更大的贡献\n四川省康定市炉城镇向阳街"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":330,"aggregated":"四川里伍铜业股份有限公司\n四川里伍铜业股份有限公司前身为四川省里伍铜矿\n系由甘孜州国资委实际控制的国有控股企业\n公司主要从事有色金属采选\n销售并兼营水电资源的开发\n公司主营业务为自有铜矿开采及选矿业务\n公司注册地址及办公总部设在康定\n主体矿山位于甘孜藏族自治州九龙县魁多镇\n公司总部下设十个职能部门\n一座直属矿山和一个项目部\n丹巴协作铂镍公司等五家子公司及一家参股商业银行\n其中大专及以上学历的员工\n公司以其良好的经营业绩成为甘孜州的纳税大户\n进入四川省工业企业最大规模\n四川省工业企业最佳效益\n全国危机矿山接替资源找矿专项先进集体\n公司所属的里伍铜矿被四川省人民政府授予四川省重点建设先进单位称号\n中国地质调查局地质科技奖二等奖\n年度科技创新工作先进单位\n年度四川省企业技术中心\n公司控股子公司雅砻江矿业被评为\n公司拥有的里伍铜矿和黑牛洞铜矿均被自然资源部纳入全国绿色矿山名录\n利用自身在资源开发上的人才\n运作好更多优势的开发项目\n把企业进一步做强做优做大\n使里伍公司长期繁荣昌盛\n为富民安康做出更大的贡献\n四川省康定市炉城镇向阳街","cwd":"/home/kensoulstar/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776878178223}}
{"type":"message","id":"f419c1bf","parentId":"352c644b","timestamp":"2026-04-22T17:16:29.432Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good, I'm getting useful Chinese text now. Let me also try to get more specific information like founding year, registered capital, stock code, etc. from the website and related pages.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"894725667","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# Get more detailed info - looking for dates, numbers, etc.\ncurl -sL --connect-timeout 15 \"https://www.lwty.com/Single_index_id_1.shtml\" | python3 -c \"\nimport sys\nimport re\ncontent = sys.stdin.read()\n\n# Look for patterns with years and numbers\npatterns = [\n    r'建[设立]于?(\\d{4})年',\n    r'(?:成立|创建)\\s*(\\d{2,4}[-年]\\d+)',\n    r'(?:注册资本|注册资金)[：:](.+?)元',\n    r'上市时间.*?(\\d{4})',\n    r'(?:股票代码)[：:]([\\d]+)',\n]\n\nfor p in patterns:\n    matches = re.findall(p, content)\n    if matches:\n        print(f'{p}: {matches}')\n\n# Also look for any date-like patterns\ndates = re.findall(r'(\\d{4})[-/年](\\d{1,2})[-/月]?(\\d{1,2})?', content)\nif dates:\n    print('Dates found:', dates[:5])\n\" 2>/dev/null","timeout":20}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"lmstudio","model":"qwen3.6-35b-a3b-claude-4.6-opus-reasoning-distilled@q4_k_m","usage":{"input":44111,"output":378,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":44489,"cost":{"input":0.088222,"output":0.004536,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.092758}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776878178435,"responseId":"chatcmpl-d43n23azgn9n2v97x9j38o"}}
