{"type":"message","id":"39cd828f","parentId":"2931fab7","timestamp":"2026-04-22T17:17:03.208Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"462288897","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"关键词: \n描述: \n• 四川里伍铜业股份有限公司前身为四川省里伍铜矿，始建于1988年，1998年完成股份制改造\n• 现注册资本为22550万元，系由甘孜州国资委实际控制的国有控股企业。公司主要从事有色金属采选、销售并兼营水电资源的开发，公司主营业务为自有铜矿开采及选矿业务，主要产品为铜精矿。\n• 公司注册地址及办公总部设在康定，成都设有第二办公区，主体矿山位于甘孜藏族自治州九龙县魁多镇、烟袋镇境内。公司总部下设十个职能部门、一座直属矿山和一个项目部。旗下有雅砻江矿业公司、里铜电力公司、金伯利地勘公司、丹巴协作铂镍公司等五家子公司及一家参股商业银行。现有正式在册员工870人，其中大专及以...\n• 经过多年的发展，公司以其良好的经营业绩成为甘孜州的纳税大户，进入四川省工业企业最大规模500强、四川省工业企业最佳效益100强行列，公司被国务院评为\n• ，公司所属的里伍铜矿被四川省人民政府授予四川省重点建设先进单位称号，公司先后获得\n• 等多项荣誉，公司控股子公司雅砻江矿业被评为\n• 。2020年，公司拥有的里伍铜矿和黑牛洞铜矿均被自然资源部纳入全国绿色矿山名录。\n• 以人为本、科技创新、稳定生产、规范管理、抓住机遇、促进发展\n• 为指导思想，不断深化改革、加强管理、挖潜增效，在努力抓好生产经营、争取更大效益的同时，在州委、州政府的领导下，在地方各级党委、政府支持下，把握机遇，利用自身在资源开发上的人才、资金、技术优势，争取到、运作好更多优势的开发项目，把企业进一步做强做优做大，使里伍公司长期繁荣昌盛，为富民安康做出更大..."}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":88,"aggregated":"关键词: \n描述: \n• 四川里伍铜业股份有限公司前身为四川省里伍铜矿，始建于1988年，1998年完成股份制改造\n• 现注册资本为22550万元，系由甘孜州国资委实际控制的国有控股企业。公司主要从事有色金属采选、销售并兼营水电资源的开发，公司主营业务为自有铜矿开采及选矿业务，主要产品为铜精矿。\n• 公司注册地址及办公总部设在康定，成都设有第二办公区，主体矿山位于甘孜藏族自治州九龙县魁多镇、烟袋镇境内。公司总部下设十个职能部门、一座直属矿山和一个项目部。旗下有雅砻江矿业公司、里铜电力公司、金伯利地勘公司、丹巴协作铂镍公司等五家子公司及一家参股商业银行。现有正式在册员工870人，其中大专及以...\n• 经过多年的发展，公司以其良好的经营业绩成为甘孜州的纳税大户，进入四川省工业企业最大规模500强、四川省工业企业最佳效益100强行列，公司被国务院评为\n• ，公司所属的里伍铜矿被四川省人民政府授予四川省重点建设先进单位称号，公司先后获得\n• 等多项荣誉，公司控股子公司雅砻江矿业被评为\n• 。2020年，公司拥有的里伍铜矿和黑牛洞铜矿均被自然资源部纳入全国绿色矿山名录。\n• 以人为本、科技创新、稳定生产、规范管理、抓住机遇、促进发展\n• 为指导思想，不断深化改革、加强管理、挖潜增效，在努力抓好生产经营、争取更大效益的同时，在州委、州政府的领导下，在地方各级党委、政府支持下，把握机遇，利用自身在资源开发上的人才、资金、技术优势，争取到、运作好更多优势的开发项目，把企业进一步做强做优做大，使里伍公司长期繁荣昌盛，为富民安康做出更大...","cwd":"/home/kensoulstar/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776878223203}}
{"type":"message","id":"11f81b52","parentId":"39cd828f","timestamp":"2026-04-22T17:17:15.023Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good, I have a lot of useful information now. Let me also check the \"发展历程\" (development history) page for more details about the company's timeline and stock listing information.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"684868134","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# Get development history page content\ncurl -sL --connect-timeout 15 \"https://www.lwty.com/Single_index_id_73.shtml\" > /tmp/lwty_history.html\nfile /tmp/lwty_history.html\n\npython3 << 'PYEOF'\nimport re\n\nwith open('/tmp/lwty_history.html', 'r', encoding='utf-8') as f:\n    content = f.read()\n\n# Extract Chinese text blocks\nchinese_blocks = re.findall(r'[\\u4e00-\\u9fff\\u3000-\\u303f\\uff00-\\uffef][\\u4e00-\\u9fff\\u3000-\\u303f\\uff00-\\uffef\\s\\-·，。！、；：（）《》\\d]{15,}', content)\n\n# Deduplicate and print\nseen = set()\nfor block in chinese_blocks:\n    cleaned = block.strip()\n    if len(cleaned) > 20 and cleaned not in seen:\n        seen.add(cleaned)\n        display = cleaned if len(cleaned) < 150 else cleaned[:147] + '...'\n        print(f\"• {display}\")\n\nPYEOF","timeout":30}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"lmstudio","model":"qwen3.6-35b-a3b-claude-4.6-opus-reasoning-distilled@q4_k_m","usage":{"input":46452,"output":387,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":46839,"cost":{"input":0.092904,"output":0.004644,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.097548}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776878223418,"responseId":"chatcmpl-pm6frji4xj22kwshzpxed"}}
{"type":"message","id":"f1db3cd5","parentId":"11f81b52","timestamp":"2026-04-22T17:17:15.700Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"684868134","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"/tmp/lwty_history.html: HTML document, Unicode text, UTF-8 text, with very long lines (3339), with CRLF, CR, LF line terminators\n• 年，由中国有色金属工业总公司和甘孜州人民政府共同出资筹建四川省里伍铜矿。\n• 年完成了基本建设进入试生产阶段，1995年9月，里伍铜矿日处理原矿500吨的采选生产线正式竣工投产。\n• 年，完成了股份制改造四川里伍铜业股份有限公司成立。\n• 年，公司进行劳动用工制度改革，进行了全员国有企业身份转换，进一步优化股权结构，调动了员工生产积极性。\n• 年，九龙县属龙财矿业矿山资产对公司增资，九龙县国资公司成为公司第二大股东。此次增资为里伍片区资源整合和勘查开发奠定了基础。\n• 年，收购国土资源部成都地质矿产研究所在里伍铜业外围的探矿权。几年来，公司累计投入2亿多元在里伍周边开展找矿工作，为实现\n• 发展目标奠定了坚实基础。公司的铜矿找矿成果完成四川省\n• 年，成立九龙县里铜电力有限责任公司，开展三垭河梯级电站水电开发。目前已全部并网发电。\n• 年，公司为改善产品结构，拓展产业布局，联合收购了丹巴县协作铂镍有限责任公司。\n• 年，全资收购四川金伯利地质勘查有限公司，使公司矿产资源开发的产业配置更趋科学合理，公司资源勘查管理工作迈上了新的台阶。\n• 年初，为适应公司发展、产业布局和企业组织架构的变化，公司试行集团化管理和管理流程再造。\n• 年，上市辅导机构进驻公司，上市前期工作正式启动。\n• 年1月18日，公司总部搬迁揭牌仪式在康定举行。\n• 年，外围找矿提交黑牛洞中型富铜矿储量报告，雅砻江矿业有限责任公司成立，黑牛洞铜矿1500吨\n• 年，外围找矿提交中咀小型富铜矿储量报告，中咀铜矿开发项目部成立。"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":652,"aggregated":"/tmp/lwty_history.html: HTML document, Unicode text, UTF-8 text, with very long lines (3339), with CRLF, CR, LF line terminators\n• 年，由中国有色金属工业总公司和甘孜州人民政府共同出资筹建四川省里伍铜矿。\n• 年完成了基本建设进入试生产阶段，1995年9月，里伍铜矿日处理原矿500吨的采选生产线正式竣工投产。\n• 年，完成了股份制改造四川里伍铜业股份有限公司成立。\n• 年，公司进行劳动用工制度改革，进行了全员国有企业身份转换，进一步优化股权结构，调动了员工生产积极性。\n• 年，九龙县属龙财矿业矿山资产对公司增资，九龙县国资公司成为公司第二大股东。此次增资为里伍片区资源整合和勘查开发奠定了基础。\n• 年，收购国土资源部成都地质矿产研究所在里伍铜业外围的探矿权。几年来，公司累计投入2亿多元在里伍周边开展找矿工作，为实现\n• 发展目标奠定了坚实基础。公司的铜矿找矿成果完成四川省\n• 年，成立九龙县里铜电力有限责任公司，开展三垭河梯级电站水电开发。目前已全部并网发电。\n• 年，公司为改善产品结构，拓展产业布局，联合收购了丹巴县协作铂镍有限责任公司。\n• 年，全资收购四川金伯利地质勘查有限公司，使公司矿产资源开发的产业配置更趋科学合理，公司资源勘查管理工作迈上了新的台阶。\n• 年初，为适应公司发展、产业布局和企业组织架构的变化，公司试行集团化管理和管理流程再造。\n• 年，上市辅导机构进驻公司，上市前期工作正式启动。\n• 年1月18日，公司总部搬迁揭牌仪式在康定举行。\n• 年，外围找矿提交黑牛洞中型富铜矿储量报告，雅砻江矿业有限责任公司成立，黑牛洞铜矿1500吨\n• 年，外围找矿提交中咀小型富铜矿储量报告，中咀铜矿开发项目部成立。","cwd":"/home/kensoulstar/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776878235695}}
{"type":"message","id":"0b5063a1","parentId":"f1db3cd5","timestamp":"2026-04-22T17:17:30.019Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I have good information now. Let me also try to find the stock code and listing date from other sources, as it seems like the company went public but I need to verify. Let me also look for any additional details about their business operations.\n\nBased on what I've gathered:\n- Founded in 1988 as Sichuan Liwu Copper Mine\n- Completed shareholding reform in 1998, becoming Sichuan Liwu Copper Industry Co., Ltd.\n- Registered capital: 22550万元 (225.5 million yuan)\n\n\n- Controlled by Ganzi Prefecture SASAC\n- Headquarters located in Kangding with a secondary office in Chengdu and main mining operations in Jiulong County\n\nI'm also seeing that the company expanded into hydropower through its subsidiary Li Tong Power Company, established several other subsidiaries including geological survey and platinum-nickel ventures, maintains 870 employees, and has been recognized as one of Sichuan's top industrial enterprises by both scale and profitability.\n\nThey've received multiple honors from the State Council and provincial government, with both their copper mines added to the national green mine registry in 2020. The company completed shareholding reform back in 1998, went through labor system changes later on, and has been working toward going public—though I need to verify when that actually happened since my earlier search came up empty.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"322425658","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# Search for stock listing info using eastmoney API with different parameters\ncurl -sL --connect-timeout 15 \"https://searchapi.eastmoney.com/api/suggest/get?input=%E9%87%8C%E4%BC%8D&type=3&count=5\" 2>/dev/null | python3 -m json.tool 2>/dev/null | head -50","timeout":20}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"lmstudio","model":"qwen3.6-35b-a3b-claude-4.6-opus-reasoning-distilled@q4_k_m","usage":{"input":47260,"output":710,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":47970,"cost":{"input":0.09451999999999999,"output":0.00852,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.10303999999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776878235903,"responseId":"chatcmpl-qhkh2osogfdwggeynrulsn"}}
{"type":"message","id":"253ace82","parentId":"0b5063a1","timestamp":"2026-04-22T17:17:30.254Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"322425658","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n    \"Portfolio\": {\n        \"Data\": [\n            {\n                \"zuheName\": \"\\u6a21\\u62df\\u7ec4\\u54089434375\",\n                \"url\": \"http://group.eastmoney.com/other,252940100000234375.html\"\n            },\n            {\n                \"zuheName\": \"\\u6a21\\u62df\\u7ec4\\u54084779258\",\n                \"url\": \"http://group.eastmoney.com/other,250470100000079258.html\"\n            }\n        ],\n        \"Status\": 0,\n        \"Message\": \"\\u6210\\u529f\",\n        \"TotalCount\": 2,\n        \"BizCode\": \"\",\n        \"BizMsg\": \"\"\n    }\n}"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":211,"aggregated":"{\n    \"Portfolio\": {\n        \"Data\": [\n            {\n                \"zuheName\": \"\\u6a21\\u62df\\u7ec4\\u54089434375\",\n                \"url\": \"http://group.eastmoney.com/other,252940100000234375.html\"\n            },\n            {\n                \"zuheName\": \"\\u6a21\\u62df\\u7ec4\\u54084779258\",\n                \"url\": \"http://group.eastmoney.com/other,250470100000079258.html\"\n            }\n        ],\n        \"Status\": 0,\n        \"Message\": \"\\u6210\\u529f\",\n        \"TotalCount\": 2,\n        \"BizCode\": \"\",\n        \"BizMsg\": \"\"\n    }\n}","cwd":"/home/kensoulstar/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776878250249}}
{"type":"message","id":"e43db37c","parentId":"253ace82","timestamp":"2026-04-22T17:17:44.207Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me try searching for the stock code more specifically. Based on what I know about Chinese A-share stocks, codes starting with 300xxx are for ChiNext (创业板), and those in the 002xxx range are for Shenzhen Main Board. Let me search a bit more.\n\nActually, let me just compile what I have from the website so far - it's quite comprehensive. The company may not be publicly listed yet based on my searches, or might have a different listing status.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"134545430","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# Try to get more info from announcements page\ncurl -sL --connect-timeout 15 \"https://www.lwty.com/News_lists_sort_14.shtml\" > /tmp/lwty_announcements.html\npython3 << 'PYEOF'\nimport re\n\nwith open('/tmp/lwty_announcements.html', 'r', encoding='utf-8') as f:\n    content = f.read()\n\n# Look for any listing-related announcements\nlisting_patterns = [\n    r'上市.*?(?:成功|获批|公告)',\n    r'SME|创业板|主板|科创板',\n    r'A股|港股',\n]\n\nfor pattern in listing_patterns:\n    matches = re.findall(pattern, content)\n    if matches:\n        for m in matches[:3]:\n            print(f\"Found '{pattern}': {m}\")\n\n# Also extract title links that might be relevant\ntitles = re.findall(r'<a[^>]*>([^<]+)</a>', content)\nrelevant_titles = [t for t in titles if any(x in t for x in ['上市', '公告', '股东', '财务'])]\nfor t in relevant_titles[:10]:\n    print(f\"Title: {t.strip()}\")\n\nPYEOF","timeout":20}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"lmstudio","model":"qwen3.6-35b-a3b-claude-4.6-opus-reasoning-distilled@q4_k_m","usage":{"input":47914,"output":514,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":48428,"cost":{"input":0.095828,"output":0.006168,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.101996}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776878250479,"responseId":"chatcmpl-sevcz3miknhhi9hdpxsu1"}}
